      "description": "AptaSelect identifies high-frequency aptamer candidate sequences from paired-end FASTQ files produced by SELEX experiments. The pipeline joins paired-end reads, applies three sequential pattern-based filtering stages (Selection, 1st Sort, 2nd Sort), and aggregates and ranks sequences by frequency at each stage.",
